# Testing Rule

Prioritize tests for:

- Token generation and validation

- Log ingestion auth

- Alert destination CRUD

- Alert aggregation grouping

- Alert sender routing

- Controller integration flow

Use:

- JUnit 5

- Spring Boot Test

- MockMvc or TestRestTemplate

- Testcontainers for Postgres integration tests

- Mockito for unit-level service routing tests

Do not call real Slack/Discord webhooks from automated tests.

Webhook delivery can be manually tested through the test endpoint.